#

Bourbon-Glazed Pork Tenderloin

40 min
$12.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickSavoryComfort Food

Description

Tender pork tenderloin coated in a sweet and savory bourbon glaze, perfect for a quick yet impressive dinner!

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 pound
  • bourbon: 1/2 cup
  • brown sugar: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: to taste
